# design-sync (claude.ai/design)
# The sync INPUTS under .design-sync/ are committed on purpose — config, notes,
# conventions, authored previews, the lib fork and the self-hosted fonts. Only
# generated output and staged tooling are ignored.
.ds-sync/
ds-bundle/
.design-sync/.cache/
.design-sync/learnings/
.design-sync/node_modules
